SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT inventory_trx.Product_Id, inventory_trx.Trx_Type, inventory_trx.Property_String, inventory_trx.SKU, inventory_trx.Trx_Source, inventory_trx.Market_Owner, inventory_trx.Transaction_Date, inventory_trx.Location, inventory_trx.Quantity, inventory_trx.UOM, inventory_trx.Product_Name, inventory_trx.Transaction_Time, inventory_trx.Comment FROM inventory_trx WHERE inventory_trx.Market_Owner = :1 :2 :3 :4

ExpSyntax.val: IF (Trim ({1,4})<>'',IF (Trim ({1,5})<>'','AND Contact.'&Trim ({1,5})&' LIKE '&{1,26}&'%'&Trim ({1,4})&'%'&{1,26},' AND (Contact.Contact_Last_Name LIKE '&{1,26}&Trim ({1,4})&'%'&{1,26}&' OR Contact.Contact_First_Name LIKE '&{1,26}&Trim ({1,4})&'%'&{1,26}&' OR Contact.Contact_Organization_Name LIKE '&{1,26}&Trim ({1,4})&'%'&{1,26}),'')
IF (Trim ({0,2})='','ORDER BY Inventory_trx.Internal_Seq_Number DESC',' ORDER BY Inventory_trx.'&Trim ({0,2}))

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM inventory_trx WHERE inventory_trx.Market_Owner = :1 :2 :3
